title: O'Neill Evolution 2011 - Halfpipe Men Finals
description: O'Neill Evolution 2011 Men Halfpipe Finals. Swiss riders take up the podium. In 1st Christian Haller, 2nd Iouri Podladtchikov and 3rd place 16 year old Jan Scherrer. Watch this amazing highlight clip.
